ramName attribute (updating the parameter reference), with before and after code examples provided to illustrate the changes.\n\nFor the second section on testing procedures, I'm seeing the step-by-step process for verifying the user info update feature works correctly, including notes about UI limitations like the back button on the confirmation screen not being functional and alternative navigation paths available from the completion screen. I'm modifying the JSP file to redirect the update link to a different action and change the parameter name to match the new target structure.\n\nNow I need to verify the changes work correctly by testing the user information workflow—searching for users, updating their details, confirming the changes, and verifying the updates persist in the system.\n\nI notice the back button on the confirmation screen isn't functional since it hasn't been implemented yet, and users can only navigate away from the completion screen through header or footer links.\n\nNow I'm working through the search hints and identifying which parts are specific to the sample application versus general documentation. I need to distinguish between procedural steps that are tutorial-focused and the actual configuration changes needed—like the JSP file modifications, URI updates, and parameter name adjustments that form the core of the implementation work.","signature":""}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":2,"cache_creation_input_tokens":21183,"cache_read_input_tokens":29889,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":21183,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0},"output_tokens":8},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"9ccfc5d6-9d4b-45ce-871e-ed262b75a233","uuid":"33fae7d0-ebb6-47c9-a573-4d5bce5c019b"}
{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-sonnet-4-6","id":"msg_bdrk_01Ry9zRoJDEornXsa4gyHL9A","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"toolu_bdrk_01E4fyBfoa94xUTGuoLiD3tF","name":"StructuredOutput","input":{"id":"web-application-09_confirm_operation","title":"動作確認をする為のサンプルアプリケーションの修正と動作確認の実施","no_knowledge_content":false,"official_doc_urls":[],"index":[{"id":"s1","title":"動作確認をする為のサンプルアプリケーションの修正","hints":["n:submitLink","n:param","W11AC0101.jsp","JSP修正","サンプルアプリケーション修正","更新リンク","paramName変更","uri属性変更"]},{"id":"s2","title":"動作確認の実施","hints":["動作確認","ユーザ情報更新","更新確認画面","更新完了画面","戻るボタン","ヘッダ","フッタ"]}],"sections":{"s1":"## 動作確認をする為のサンプルアプリケーションの修正\n\n**修正ファイル**: `W11AC0101.jsp`\n\n`n:submitLink` タグの以下を変更する:\n\n- `uri` 属性: `/action/ss11AC/W11AC03Action/RW11AC0301` → `/action/ss11AC/W11ACXXAction/RW11ACXX01`\n- `n:param` の `paramName` 属性: `W11AC03.systemAccount.userId` → `W11ACXX.operationTargetUserId`\n\n修正後:\n\n```jsp\n<%-- 【説明】更新リンクの遷移先を変更 --%>\n<td><n:submitLink uri=\"/action/ss11AC/W11ACXXAction/RW11ACXX01\" name=\"showUpdate_${count}\">\n                更新\n                <%-- ～中略～ --%>\n                <%-- 【説明】パラメータ名の変更 --%>\n                <n:param paramName=\"W11ACXX.operationTargetUserId\" name=\"row.userId\" />\n            </n:submitLink></td>\n```","s2":"## 動作確認の実施\n\n1. ユーザ情報照会画面で一覧検索し、検索結果の **更新** リンクをクリック\n2. ユーザ情報更新画面で入力フォームの値を変更して **確認** ボタンを押下\n3. ユーザ情報更新確認画面で更新する値が表示されていることを確認し、**確定** ボタンを押下\n4. ユーザ情報更新完了画面で更新した値が表示されていることを確認\n5. 再度一覧検索を行い、ユーザ情報が更新されていることを確認\n\n> **注意**: ユーザ情報更新確認画面の **戻る** ボタンは実装されていないため動作しない。\n\n> **注意**: ユーザ情報更新完了画面からは、ヘッダまたはフッタのリンクをクリックして別の画面へ移動できる。"}}}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":2,"cache_creation_input_tokens":21183,"cache_read_input_tokens":29889,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":21183,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0},"output_tokens":8},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"9ccfc5d6-9d4b-45ce-871e-ed262b75a233","uuid":"7f773df4-3568-4b0b-bc5b-4270dae1052e"}
